PortSystem          1.0

name                gource
version             0.40
categories          devel
platforms           darwin
license             GPL-3+
maintainers         phw openmaintainer

description         Version Control Visualization Tool

long_description    Gource is a tool that can be used to visualize who \
                    committed when, and to which files. It supports git, CVS, \
                    Mercurial, Bazaar, and svn.

homepage            http://code.google.com/p/gource/
master_sites        googlecode

checksums           rmd160  b0f4aa96e838b5db2c6d93a6d10a398b4ff914d6 \
                    sha256  9c890a926bb3bab8ea3e546c1357488e5a5034d1ea9402afc654cb7e00ccd112

